Happy Fathers Day to all the Fathers out there & especially to my husband Jeremy! 💚 
.
He became a teen dad when he was very young and hasn’t stopped working hard to provide and loving his kids ever since his “Fatherhood” began all those years ago! He is a man who carries the weight of the world on his shoulders, gives everything, and asks for nothing. 💚 Our boys are blessed to have him as their father. 💚

Happy Anniversary to my best friend & partner in life! 🥰❤️ We have grown so much over the years & to think when we first got together in our 20s we thought we was all the way grown and knew it all. 🤣 I’m sure we will look back when we’re in our 50s and say the same thing about where we are now. ☺️ But I’m thankful I get to grow, succeed, cry, laugh, stumble, fall, and get back up with you Mr Randall. ❤️
I pray God blesses us with at least 80 more years on this earth & most definitely an eternity after! ❤️🙏🏻
